  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/smartphones/\" rel=\"tag\">智能手机</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2014/02/14/htc-all-updates-flagship-device-two-years/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/99ac0c379fb8da0ec5570310ef2d6975/one.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 358px;\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n \n<div>美国 HTC 产品团队除了在 Reddit 上被问到<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/14/htc-windows-phone-8x/\">有关 Windows Phone 的问题</a>之外，当然有被问到 Android 业务吧。他们在问答期间确认了会为未来所有在北美市场推出的旗舰级手机，在上市后两年内继续带来「所有主要 Android 升级」。根据 HTC 的行为纪录，<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/OneX/\">One X</a> 这部「曾经旗舰」的手机的确在推出差不多两年之后<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/13/htc-one-x-no-kitkat/\">停止更新</a>，最终的官方版本是 Android 4.2。说到他们将会推出的旗舰机方面，大概至少有 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/M8/\">M8</a> 吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/02/14/htc-all-updates-flagship-device-two-years/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.reddit.com/r/Android/comments/1xxjfx/hi_were_the_htc_usa_product_team_amaa/\">Reddit</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/15/htc-all-updates-flagship-device-two-years/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20830844/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/15/htc-all-updates-flagship-device-two-years/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
